		<title>Nigeria licenced 46 telecom challengers to rival MTN and Airtel. Few have taken off.</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/06/05/why-nigerias-mvno-dream-is-struggling-to-connect/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Frank Eleanya]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 13:07:08 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Features]]></category>
